metadata.name: Sinister Power
metadata.description:
They came with ruinous machines and laid waste.  This city is already dead, and they are here to drain what's left of the wasting corpse.

As we are caught in their sight, eyes burn flesh from bone atom by atom, speaking "We are tasked by providence and permanence."

This sinister power becomes the End.

Mint link: https://app.manifold.xyz/c/sinister-power
